<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulrich, Bischof von Brixen und Kanzler von Österreich, Eckhard von Vilanders, Marschall von Österreich, Burkhard von Rabenstein, Hofmeister von Österreich, Hans von Freundsberg, Ritter, und Heinrich VI. von Rottenburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass er Hans Camerer, Diener der Stadt, und Konrad Prager, Bürger zu Nürnberg, zur Vermittlung wegen der von Friedrich von Fladnitz und Ulrich von Weißpriach beschlagnahmten Waren Nürnberger Kaufleute zu den Herzögen von Österreich entsandt hat, und bittet sie um Fürsprache.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_43" id="21r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_43_r1l21"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Bẏſchof cʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough"> P </del> Brichſen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l22">von ~ Oſterreich kancʒler </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_43_r1l23">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir ſenden cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> hercʒog <expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l24"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Oſterreich <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> / Hanſen <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l25">Prager <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger vnd diener cʒu reden von der hab vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l26">kaufmanſchaft wegen / als Jr diener her <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von flednicʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l27">vnd her <expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von VVeẏſpriach / den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in Jren <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> herſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l28">vnd gepieten <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd auch etlıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabeẏ ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l29">fangen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> diener </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l30">dienern / 
<del rend="strikethrough">ew </del> gen <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ von Oſterreiche ewr </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_44" id="21v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l1">günſtige hilff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gnedıklich bevveiſen wöllet / durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l2"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen / Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><pb facs="#facs_44"/>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l3"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Eckhart <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> villanders / <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> fridrichs von <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>reıch</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_44_r1l4"><expan>Marſchalk</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l5"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burkhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von Rabenſteın <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l6"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> von </del> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>rcʒog</expan> <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Oſterreich <expan>hofmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_44_r1l7"><expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l8"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hanſen von <expan>freuntſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l9"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / etc <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_43" id="21r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, byschof czu Brichsen,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Osterreich kanczler </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden czu
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog <expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Osterreich
                            <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> Hansen <expan>Camr<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>Conr<ex>aden</ex></expan> Prager,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger und diener, czu reden von der hab
                        und kaufmanschaft wegen, als ir diener, her <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        von Flednicz und her <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Weyspriach, den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in iren
                            <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, herschaft und gepieten
                                <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch etlich die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey gefangen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
                        ir <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und dienern gen
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Osterreiche ewr <pb facs="#facs_44" id="21v"/>günstige hilff und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gnediklich beweisen
                        wöllet durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen, als etc. Das wöllen
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><pb facs="#facs_44"/>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Eckhart <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Villanders,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Fridrichs von
                            <expan>Ost<ex>er</ex>reich</expan>
<expan>marschalk</expan>, <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Burkhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von Rabenstein,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rczog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Osterreich,
                            <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>,
                            <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen von
                            <expan>Freuntsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Rotemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc.
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
